title: Wall Street Breakfast: The Week Ahead
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Auto sales are expected to hit high in a new report, while Tesla (TSLA) could smash prepandamic numbers. The September U.S. jobs report will drop, and the labor market is showing no signs of slowing down. And, a special event this week will showcase how business practices will evolve in the metaverse.
